    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      OTHER
      A different error which we know what it is but doesn't fit into any of the other two categories.
      PROTOCOL
      A protocol error means some kind of problem with the response we got.
      TRANSPORT
      A transport error is any kind of error that's related to the transport layer like a refused connection or a 404 error etc.
      UNKNOWN
      An error that we didn't expect and have no idea what it is.
